blog/how-many-gb-in-tb-quick-guide/#section--2">What Is a Gigabyte?</a>
        <a class=3D"tutorial__menu-link" href=3D"https://driveuploader.com/=
blog/how-many-gb-in-tb-quick-guide/#section--3">What Is a Terabyte?</a>
        <a class=3D"tutorial__menu-link" href=3D"https://driveuploader.com/=
blog/how-many-gb-in-tb-quick-guide/#section--4">How Many Gigabytes in a Ter=
abyte?</a>
